nodes.title: Positive
widgets_values: A highly detailed macro photograph of a futuristic mechanical flower blooming on a moss-covered branch in an ancient forest at sunrise. The flower's petals are constructed from iridescent glass and polished gold, with intricate internal gears and glowing blue optical fibers visible inside. Dew droplets cling to the metal and glass surfaces, catching the golden morning light filtering through the trees. The background is a soft, magical bokeh of light and forest greens. Cinematic lighting, rich textures, shallow depth of field.
